data.description: Looking for a small piece of paradise that feels like the country but is still close to the city? Well, here it is! This 4 bed 2.5 bath home sits on 2.39 acres! Perfect size for goats or chickens!! The house is set up for entertaining, with a huge deck overlooking the back yard, a pool table/ game room and a built in bar! Pull up a stool and watch the game just like your're out on the town!  The entire house is styled in rustic farmhouse look with cedar and metal everywhere! Come this unique property and make it yours!
